{"id":"entities/oregon","title":"Oregon","type":"entities","html":"<h1>Oregon</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>The home-state container — Yahir's <strong>birth-to-Austin geography</strong>: childhood in <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/grants-pass-or\">Grants Pass</a> (southern OR), undergrad at <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/osu\">OSU</a> in <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/corvallis-or\">Corvallis</a> (mid-valley), summer internship in <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/portland-or\">Portland</a>, scholarship + legal infrastructure (Renaissance, Ford Family Foundation, IDA, SPO) all routed through Oregon-state programs. Oregon is the <strong>structural prequel</strong> to the Austin chapter — every funding source, every formative mentor, every roommate map originates here.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2>Sub-geography</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/grants-pass-or\">grants pass or</a> — hometown, <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/grants-pass-teen-era\">teen era</a> anchor, <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/yahir-family\">family</a> base</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/corvallis-or\">corvallis or</a> — OSU campus, roommate eras with <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/kyle\">kyle</a> / <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/ayden\">ayden</a>, <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/corvallis-crypto-club\">corvallis crypto club</a> founding</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/portland-or\">portland or</a> — internship orbit, <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/alexandria-nagy\">Alexandria</a> base, summer-2019 launchpad</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Oregon as funding stack</h2>\n<p>The financial spine of pre-Austin Yahir was almost entirely Oregon-state programs:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/renaissance-scholarship\">Renaissance Scholarship</a> (via <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/diana-hoff\">diana hoff</a>)</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/ford-family-foundation\">Ford Family Foundation</a> (via <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/zane\">zane</a>)</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/al-forthan\">Al Forthan</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/jcef\">JCEF</a> (via <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/quin\">quin</a>)</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/ida-individual-development-account\">Oregon IDA Initiative</a> (<a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2025-12-05-ida-translations\">2025 12 05 ida translations</a> — translation work for the program)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Oregon as legal scaffolding</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/oregon-courts\">Oregon courts / SPO</a> — <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2025-03-12-stalking-packet\">Stalking Protective Order</a> in the post-<a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/sam-solum\">Sam</a> arc</li>\n<li>IDA program is itself a state-administered match-savings vehicle</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Source summaries</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2019-08-11-finish-packing-shit-in-morning\">2019 08 11 finish packing shit in morning</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2019-09-10-low-key-writing-this-to-end\">2019 09 10 low key writing this to end</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2025-03-12-stalking-packet\">2025 03 12 stalking packet</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2025-12-05-ida-translations\">2025 12 05 ida translations</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2021-04-19-why-osu\">2021 04 19 why osu</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2024-05-13-things\">2024 05 13 things</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Connections</h2>\n<p><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/grants-pass-or\">grants pass or</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/corvallis-or\">corvallis or</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/portland-or\">portland or</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/osu\">osu</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/oregon-courts\">oregon courts</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/renaissance-scholarship\">renaissance scholarship</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/ford-family-foundation\">ford family foundation</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/ida-individual-development-account\">ida individual development account</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/al-forthan\">al forthan</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/jcef\">jcef</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/austin-tx\">austin tx</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/the-austin-thesis\">the austin thesis</a></p>\n","related":[{"id":"summaries/2025-06-29-uclamphmissiondraft","label":"2025 06 29 Uclamphmissiondraft"},{"id":"summaries/2025-12-05-ida-translations","label":"2025 12 05 Ida Translations"},{"id":"entities/al-forthan","label":"Al Forthan Memorial Scholarship"},{"id":"entities/alexandria-nagy","label":"Alexandria Nagy"},{"id":"entities/austin-tx","label":"Austin, Texas"},{"id":"entities/ayden","label":"Ayden"},{"id":"summaries/2025-08-22-camping-list-roommate-split","label":"Camping List + Roommate Rent Split (Aug 2025)"},{"id":"concepts/colle